{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Try the demo now! In the House of Lost Souls demo, one chapter is available where you can explore a mysterious house. The game focuses on atmospheric exploration, with no clear objectives - just listen to the character's voice, explore every corner and pay attention to details that might be important.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3535680/extras/1-gif.gif?t=1740078816\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this chapter, you'll touch a piece of Jack's past, where the house comes alive in distorted memories, changing your perception of reality and revealing the family's sinister secrets. You'll feel the walls fill with whispers of the past and familiar objects take on frightening meanings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3535680/extras/gif-3.gif?t=1740078816\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore, juxtapose events and try to understand what truth lies behind this illusion. Immerse yourself in the dark story and feel the disturbing atmosphere enveloping every step of the hero.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3535680/extras/2-gif.gif?t=1740078816\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><br>Game Features</u>:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Exciting story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Walking simulator game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- The mystery of the old house, which can be solved by studying old records.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- A frightening atmosphere created by sound effects that cause a constant sense of presence.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Beautiful picture that conveys the plausibility of what is happening.</p>